I've made the source of PGP 2.2, as well as MSDOS and Macintosh executables,
available for anonymous ftp from leif.thep.lu.se [130.235.92.55] in
the directory pub/Misc. Please note that this FTP site is in Sweden,Europe.

The relevant files are:

 312726 Mar 30 12:26 MacPGP22.cpt.hqx    Public Key Encryption for Macintosh
 209409 Mar 29 11:41 pgp22.zip		 New version of Pretty Good Privacy - 
					 Public Key encryption (MSDOS)
 521550 Mar 29 11:42 pgp22src.zip	 Source for PGP 2.2 (various OS's)
   7271 Mar 29 11:42 pgplegal.zip 	 Some comments on the legality of 
					 using PGP


